							Consider the following sequence of cube moves:
							<me>
								\text{EO} = (M_R U)^3 U (M_R^{-1} U)^3 U
							</me>
							Written less compactly, this move is: <m>M_R U M_R U M_R U U M_R^{-1} U M_R^{-1} U M_R^{-1} U U</m>.
						</statement>
					</heuristic>
					
					
								<exploration>
						<p>
							Consider <xref ref="cube-move-eo" />.
						</p>
						<ol>
							<li>Which cubies are affected by this move?</li>
