								In a <url href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/263178905_When_Does_Appending_the_Same_Digit_Repeatedly_on_the_Right_of_a_Positive_Integer_Generate_a_Sequence_of_Composite_Integers">recent paper</url>, Lenny Jones introduced an interesting sequence of numbers:
