					</table>
					
					
					
					<p>
						The <term>disjunction</term> of <m>P</m> and <m>Q</m>, denoted <m>P \lor Q</m> and read "<m>P</m> or <m>Q</m>", is true when <m>P</m> is true, <m>Q</m> is true, or both are true, and false otherwise. See <xref ref="table-or" />.
					</p>
					
